@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api
@authToken = YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 获取所有技能
GET {{baseUrl}}/skills
Accept: application/json

### 根据 ID 获取技能详情
GET {{baseUrl}}/skills/docx
Accept: application/json

### 创建新技能 (不传 id，系统会自动根据 name 生成 slug 作为 id)
POST {{baseUrl}}/skills
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "New Awesome Skill",
  "description": "A detailed description of the skill in English.",
  "descriptionZh": "该技能的中文详细描述。",
  "category": "productivity",
  "repository": "https://github.com/username/repo",
  "author": "Author Name",
  "tags": ["AI", "Helper", "Tool"],
  "featured": true,
  "official": false
}

### 更新技能 (提供 id 即可触发更新)
POST {{baseUrl}}/skills
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "new-awesome-skill",
  "name": "Updated Skill Name",
  "description": "Updated English description.",
  "descriptionZh": "更新后的中文描述。",
  "category": "development",
  "repository": "https://github.com/username/repo",
  "author": "Author Name",
  "tags": ["AI", "Updated"],
  "featured": false,
  "official": true
}

### 删除技能
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/skills/new-awesome-skill
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json
